              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23845948/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23845948/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3813090/" class=" " title="芒">芒</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23845948">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">学业要靠一点一滴地艰苦积累，与人相处要择善而从，避平庸而就高明。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-01-12 21:03</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                学业要靠一点一滴地艰苦积累，与人相处要择善而从，避平庸而就高明。
